Class EntityCollectionStatistics

java.lang.Object
com.github.hanyaeger.core.entities.EntityCollectionStatistics
public class EntityCollectionStatistics extends Object
An EntityCollectionStatistics is a DTO (Data Transfer Object) that contains all current values from an EntityCollection.
